{"tid":2376384,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"【Dr Stone石紀元】羽京個配音嚇成人……","createTime":"2021-01-22T17:53:57.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-07T13:13:03.000Z","uid":390261,"like":0,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"785b94ff7c12c66c4d112efb3980b82b5ec1caa1","tid":2376384,"uid":390261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T17:53:57.000Z","msg":"第一季剛剛播完沒耐 小弟就上網掃晒啲漫畫佢<br />\n有時候為咗係睇漫畫時睇得更投入 係讀裏面啲讀白時好多時都會代入番佢地把聲<br />\n第一季的角色例如千空 大樹 克羅姆等等的聲音都曾經亮過相 <br />\n不過第二季新添嘅角色就沒有 通常都要睇樣腦補把聲出嚟<br />\n例如我最鍾意嘅射手羽京 雖然佢係大人 不過生得矮矮地成個正大樣 有時又會扮下萠<br />\n所以下意識地入咗把正太男仔聲俾佢<br />\n點知尋日出第二季個時聽到個把壯年男人聲...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成個人呆咗，一直係到Replay，係到呃自己呢把吾係佢把聲<br />\n好大打擊，過咗一陣先接受到...<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n吾知動漫黨睇動畫個時會唔會有呢種打擊呢？"},{"pid":"2e0a419f774f0ae48dac83c127f9d8c367e8f7c7","tid":2376384,"uid":200529,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T18:03:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OqVxdaK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOqVxdaK.png&h=2828f9cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"606b3502bcdb35d31c0a47bea53b3f004650d53e","tid":2376384,"uid":69866,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"2e0a419f774f0ae48dac83c127f9d8c367e8f7c7","tid":2376384,"uid":200529,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T18:03:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OqVxdaK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOqVxdaK.png&h=2828f9cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T18:12:31.000Z","msg":"連登：Dr. STONE 青山走犯"},{"pid":"8943bd498be749dfdac31e757c884b52e8f5391b","tid":2376384,"uid":237038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-27T16:53:07.000Z","msg":"依家喺邊度有得睇"},{"pid":"621c8a862e6450f5cc836afca35aed0bca650c66","tid":2376384,"uid":390261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8943bd498be749dfdac31e757c884